exampleEn: The billionaire’s ostentatious lifestyle was widely criticized.
exampleUz: Milliarderning dabdabali hayoti keng tanqid qilindi.

exampleEn: She took a pragmatic approach to solving the problem.
exampleUz: U muammoni hal qilishda amaliy yondashuvni tanladi.

exampleEn: The recalcitrant student refused to follow the rules.
exampleUz: Itoatsiz o‘quvchi qoidalarga bo‘ysunishni rad etdi.

exampleEn: Her sagacious advice helped us make the right decision.
exampleUz: Uning farosatli maslahati bizga to‘g‘ri qaror qabul qilishga yordam berdi.

exampleEn: His comments were tangential to the main discussion.
exampleUz: Uning fikrlari asosiy munozaraga bevosita aloqador emas edi.

exampleEn: The pandemic created an unprecedented global crisis.
exampleUz: Pandemiya misli ko‘rilmagan global inqirozni yuzaga keltirdi.

exampleEn: New evidence vindicated the wrongly accused man.
exampleUz: Yangi dalillar nohaq ayblangan odamni oqladi.

exampleEn: The whimsical design of the house attracted tourists.
exampleUz: Uyning g‘ayrioddiy dizayni sayyohlarni o‘ziga jalb qildi.

exampleEn: Her yielding nature made her popular among her peers.
exampleUz: Uning bo‘ysunuvchan tabiati uni tengdoshlari orasida mashhur qildi.

exampleEn: He lived every day with a zestful energy.
exampleUz: U har kunni jo‘shqin energiya bilan yashadi.

exampleEn: The plot of the movie was too convoluted to follow.
exampleUz: Filmning syujeti tushunish uchun juda murakkab edi.
